        &lt;figcaption&gt;北京冬奥会开幕式在中国国家体育场“鸟巢”举行，图为从空中俯瞰的体育场。（法新社）&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;figure class="image-placeholder "&gt;&lt;img alt="" class="" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/2022-02/file7jkrint437al1wgq7fl1.jpg?VersionId=jextL6lTI_RysjIKIWN6xGiZnqhOPCED" pinger-seen="true"&gt;
