        &lt;figcaption&gt;北京冬奥会开幕式表演，画面中间是本次冬奥会的吉祥物之一“冰墩墩”。（新华社）&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;figure class="image-placeholder "&gt;&lt;img alt="" class="" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/2022-02/file7jkspyenckl2ioexooa.jpg?VersionId=hIKvXicT3bnfhGt7Gk6RG.BSXdIZhAKm" pinger-seen="true"&gt;
        &lt;figcaption&gt;冬奥会开幕式上的“冰雪五环”表演环节。（新华社）&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;figure class="image-placeholder "&gt;&lt;img alt="" class="" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/2022-02/1128330831_1643977679129_title0h.jpg?VersionId=6umiV9gAI0MutXqCa1pfVcAWX2synkRy" pinger-seen="true"&gt;
        &lt;figcaption&gt;主办国中华人民共和国国旗入场。（新华社）&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;figure class="image-placeholder "&gt;&lt;img alt="" class="" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/2022-02/1128330924_1643978182725_title0h.jpg?VersionId=V14PNPt9JHROZ6tMfacP0XuTJmI4K4eG" pinger-seen="true"&gt;
