        &lt;figcaption&gt;美国代表队入场。（法新社）&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;figure class="image-placeholder "&gt;&lt;img alt="" class="" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/2022-02/file7jktcsjfck213u0s9fhg.jpg?VersionId=fXIB6yQsOHE5qYvxM2lkR1hjXE6O8Wb7" pinger-seen="true"&gt;
        &lt;figcaption&gt;北京冬奥会开幕式表演。（路透社）&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;figure class="image-placeholder "&gt;&lt;img alt="" class="" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/2022-02/file7jktcrthety1c92cbe4b.jpg?VersionId=LxXu4DGzvTC_cJ2zVdYciN1MDVFdtndk" pinger-seen="true"&gt;
        &lt;figcaption&gt;奥林匹克会旗进入鸟巢体育场。（路透社）&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

